article_title: Value-Based Care Will Drive Aetna's Future Goals

article_metadata.description: No matter whether Aetna (AET) makes a run at rival health insurers Cigna (CI) or Humana (HUM), the coming consolidation among those picking up the tab for medical care will continue thanks in part to the move away from fee-for-service medicine to value-based care and population health.
